  "instructions": [
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine rice flour, urad dal, and salt.",
    "Gradually add yogurt and mix until a smooth batter forms.",
    "Add crumbled Wensleydale cheese and mix well.",
    "Heat ghee in a small pan and add Gujarati spice blend, let it simmer for a minute.",
    "Add the spice blend to the batter and mix.",
    "Pour the batter into a greased tandoor clay pot.",
    "Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees Celsius for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove from oven and let it cool for 5 minutes before serving."
